                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3538" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0283</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8310 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鱼与熊掌如何兼得？ ——黑暗中对话（深圳馆）的创业困局与突围</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">罗文恩，黄英，徐彩云</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黑暗中对话（Dialogue in the Dark）深圳体验馆</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共管理和社会组织</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">社会企业、创业、社会使命、商业目标、黑暗中对话</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Social enterprises; Entrepreneurship; Social mission; Business goals; Dialogue in the Dark</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，社会企业成为全球范围内的热潮现象，中国社会企业也初见端倪。本案例介绍黑暗中对话（深圳馆）两年内扭亏为盈的成长过程，探讨该社会企业如何兼顾社会使命和商业目标，实现“鱼与熊掌兼得”。虽然黑暗中对话是一家源自德国的全球性社会企业，但是落户深圳初期却是困难重重，现金流的断裂导致好几个月连租金得无法支付。在生与死的边缘，2017年深圳馆采取了多个策略来突破困境，包括降低场馆租金与推广聚焦化，服务重心向B端转移，寻求专业销售渠道，启用残障人士担任馆长以及引用“项目制管理”模式等。这些策略成功地让该社会企业转危为安，但与此同时新的隐忧开始出现，尤其是随着业务量的扩大面临残障人士专业服务供应不足的问题。在追求社会使命和商业目标的道路上，黑暗中对话（深圳馆）依然任重而道远。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Recent years, Social enterprises has become global hot issues, and in China, social enterprises began to bloom. This case aims to introduce the growth process of Dialogue in the Dark (Shenzhen) within which it turnaround to make profits in two years, and analyze how this social enterprise balanced its social mission and business goals and finally obtained both fish and bear’s paw. Although Dialogue in the Dark is a global social enterprise generated from Germany, but its encountered lots of difficulties when opening its branch in Shenzhen, the decrease of cash flow made this social enterprise incapable to pay rents. In death or life, Dialogue in the Dark (Shenzhen) adopted series of strategies to get rid of crisis, including reducing the rent of venues, turning to serve B-type customers, seeking for professional channels of distribution, appointing visually impaired people to be the head of Dialogue in the Dark (Shenzhen)
, as well as inducing project-based management. These strategies successfully pulled this social enterprise out of dangerous circumstance. However, new challenges began to emerge at the same time, which implying that the road of Dialogue in the Dark (Shenzhen) to pursuit both social mission and business goals is still long.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2017</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业学》、《非营利组织管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创业与企业成长</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-11</td>
                            </tr>
